    <title>HEXO 備忘指南（3）| Hexo 發文流程</title>
    <link href="http://kelvin820.github.io/2017/08/01/new-post/"/>
    <id>http://kelvin820.github.io/2017/08/01/new-post/</id>
    <published>2017-08-01T12:46:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-08-01T15:26:31.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="第一步-啟動nodejs"><a href="#第一步-啟動node-js" class="headerlink" title="第一步 啟動node.js"></a>第一步 啟動node.js</h2><p>我不知道為何只要terminal關閉后node就會關閉，重新執行nvm后就能順利啟動。</p>
<figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ nvm install v6<span class="number">.11</span><span class="number">.0</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="第二步-new-一個page"><a href="#第二步-new-一個page" class="headerlink" title="第二步 new 一個page"></a>第二步 new 一個page</h2><h3 id="確認hexo-是否正確啟動了node正確啟動"><a href="#確認HEXO-是否正確啟動了-node正確啟動" class="headerlink" title="確認HEXO 是否正確啟動了(node正確啟動)"></a>確認HEXO 是否正確啟動了(node正確啟動)</h3><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo -v</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="new-post"><a href="#New-Post" class="headerlink" title="New Post"></a>New Post</h3><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type"></span>"<span class="keyword">new</span><span class="type">_post_name</span>"</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>之后Hexo 會在 <strong>source/_posts</strong> 目录下面，多了一个<strong> 日期_new_post_name.md</strong>的文件。<br>打开后会看到標頭設定（如下）：<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">HEXO</span> <span class="string">備忘指南（3）|</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">發文流程</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span><span class="string">[Hexo,Markdown,教學]</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="bullet">-08</span><span class="bullet">-01</span> <span class="number">22</span><span class="string">:56:48</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">mathjax:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="草稿功能"><a href="#草稿功能" class="headerlink" title="草稿功能"></a>草稿功能</h3><p>覺得一時寫不完的blog可以利用草稿功能<br><figure class="highlight haxe"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="type">draft</span> <span class="string">"new_draft_name"</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>会在source/_drafts目录下生成一个new_draft_name.md文件。但是这个文件不被显示在页面上，链接也访问不到。</p>
<p>好不容易寫完了可以利用下列指令發佈<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo publish [layout] &lt;filemame&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="第三步-發佈到github"><a href="#第三步-發佈到github" class="headerlink" title="第三步 發佈到github"></a>第三步 發佈到github</h2><p>使用<br><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo deploy --<span class="keyword">generate</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>或<br><figure class="highlight verilog"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ heso <span class="keyword">generate</span> --deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>或是，懶人專用<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">$</span><span class="bash"> hexo g -d</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
]]></content>
    
