    <title>HEXO 備忘指南（2）| Hexo 使用的 Markdown語法備註</title>
    <link href="http://kelvin820.github.io/2017/06/27/Makrdown-howto/"/>
    <id>http://kelvin820.github.io/2017/06/27/Makrdown-howto/</id>
    <published>2017-06-27T12:46:38.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-08-01T14:53:17.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="這個是-front-matter-的寫法"><a href="#這個是-front-matter-的寫法" class="headerlink" title="這個是 front-matter 的寫法"></a>這個是 front-matter 的寫法</h2><p><code>fornt-matter</code> 的格式說明<br><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">使用的</span> <span class="string">Markdown語法備註</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">date:</span> <span class="number">2017</span><span class="bullet">-06</span><span class="bullet">-27</span> <span class="number">20</span><span class="string">:46:38</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">toc:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">categories:</span> <span class="string">Tech</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">[Hexo,Markdown,教學]</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">comments:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">mathjax:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">layout:</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">(要顯示TOC</span> <span class="string">這一欄不能寫)</span></div><div class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="文字斜體-粗體與刪除"><a href="#文字斜體、粗體與刪除" class="headerlink" title="文字斜體、粗體與刪除"></a>文字斜體、粗體與刪除</h2><p>使用 <code>_</code> 或是 <code>*</code> 表示<em>斜體</em>，使用 <code>__</code> 或是 <code>**</code> 表示<strong>粗體</strong>。</p>
<figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">*斜體* 或 <span class="keyword">_</span>斜體<span class="keyword">_</span></div><div class="line">**粗體** 或 <span class="keyword">_</span>粗體<span class="keyword">_</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>使用的 <code>~~</code> 表示。<br><figure class="highlight haml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">~~這句話刪除~~</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p><del>這句話刪除</del>  </p>
<h2 id="分隔線"><a href="#分隔線" class="headerlink" title="分隔線"></a>分隔線</h2><p>使用單行的 <code>___</code> 或是 <code>***</code> 表示。</p>
<h2 id="分級標題"><a href="#分級標題" class="headerlink" title="分級標題"></a>分級標題</h2><p>使用<code>===</code>表示一級標題，使用<code>---</code>表示二級標題。<br><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="section">這是一個一級標題</span></div><div class="line">===</div><div class="line"><span class="section">這是一個二級標題</span></div><div class="line">---</div><div class="line">### 這個可以表示三級標題</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<p>也可用<code>#</code>來定義：<br><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">/# H1  </div><div class="line">/## H2</div><div class="line">/### H3</div><div class="line">/#### H4</div><div class="line">/##### H5</div><div class="line">/###### H6</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h2 id="超鏈結寫法"><a href="#超鏈結寫法" class="headerlink" title="超鏈結寫法"></a>超鏈結寫法</h2><h3 id="文字超鏈接"><a href="#文字超鏈接" class="headerlink" title="文字超鏈接"></a>文字超鏈接</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[<span class="string">Link name</span>](<span class="link">URL</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://kelvin820.github.io/">This blog</a></p>
<h3 id="圖片超鏈結寫法"><a href="#圖片超鏈結寫法" class="headerlink" title="圖片超鏈結寫法"></a>圖片超鏈結寫法</h3><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">！[<span class="string">PIC name</span>](<span class="link">PIC URL</span>)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="http://www.cheatsheet.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Yoda-in-Star-Wars-Revenge-of-the-Sith.jpg" alt="yoda"></p>
<h3 id="youtube-內嵌法"><a href="#Youtube-內嵌法" class="headerlink" title="Youtube 內嵌法"></a>Youtube 內嵌法</h3><p>直接插入<code>iframe</code> 代碼<br><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"/js/youtube-autoresizer.js"</span>&gt;</span><span class="undefined"></span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></div><div class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">iframe</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"640"</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"360"</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://www.youtube.com/embed/HfElOZSEqn4"</span> <span class="attr">frameborder</span>=<span class="string">"0"</span> <span class="attr">allowfullscreen</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">iframe</span>&gt;</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UtsfUAHkyWQ" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe>

<h2 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h2><p>使用<code>&gt;</code> 表示<br><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">&gt;</span><span class="bash">引用內文</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<blockquote>
<p>引用內文  </p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="bullet-list"><a href="#Bullet-list" class="headerlink" title="Bullet list"></a>Bullet list</h2><p>使用<em>，+，- 搭配一個</em>空白*表示<br><figure class="highlight gcode"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">* ite<span class="name">m1</span></div><div class="line">  *ite<span class="name">m1</span><span class="number">-1</span></div><div class="line">  *ite<span class="name">m1</span><span class="number">-2</span></div><div class="line">+ ite<span class="name">m2</span></div><div class="line">  +ite<span class="name">m2</span>-</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<ul>
<li>item1<ul>
<li>item1-1</li>
<li>item1-2</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>item2<ul>
<li>item2-</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p>要使用數字的也可以，記得要數字加個<em>點</em>。Markdown厲害的是不用自己調，全寫1也可以自己排列正確。<br><figure class="highlight lsl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="number">1</span> item1</div><div class="line">  <span class="number">1.</span> item1<span class="number">-1</span></div><div class="line">  <span class="number">1.</span> item1<span class="number">-2</span></div><div class="line"><span class="number">1.</span> item2</div><div class="line">  <span class="number">1.</span> item2<span class="number">-1</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<ol>
<li>item1<ol>
<li>item1-1</li>
<li>item1-2</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>item2<ol>
<li>item2-1<h2 id="表格寫法"><a href="#表格寫法" class="headerlink" title="表格寫法"></a>表格寫法</h2></li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p>绘制表格格式如下，·<code>|</code>控制分列，<code>-</code> 控制分行，<code>:</code> 控制对齐方式。<br><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Item     </span>|<span class="string"> Value     </span>|<span class="string"> Qty   </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> :------- </span>|<span class="string"> --------: </span>|<span class="string"> :---: </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Computer </span>|<span class="string"> 1600 USD  </span>|<span class="string"> 5     </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Phone    </span>|<span class="string"> 12 USD    </span>|<span class="string"> 12    </span>|</div><div class="line">|<span class="string"> Pipe     </span>|<span class="string"> 1 USD     </span>|<span class="string"> 234   </span>|</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th style="text-align:left">Item</th>
<th style="text-align:right">Value</th>
<th style="text-align:center">Qty</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Computer</td>
<td style="text-align:right">1600 USD</td>
<td style="text-align:center">5</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Phone</td>
<td style="text-align:right">12 USD</td>
<td style="text-align:center">12</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">Pipe</td>
<td style="text-align:right">1 USD</td>
<td style="text-align:center">234</td>
</tr>
